ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would not recommend this course to a fellow student. I lost my interest in the subject after taking this course. While the reading load is appropriate, the writing load is excessive.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I had not read most of the authors on the syllabus. Definitely helped me broaden my knowledge of Spanish Romanticism and 19th century Spanish lit
It did not deepen my knowledge of the discipline. It lacks depth and breadth.
